  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/transportation/\" rel=\"tag\">交通相关</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/10/ios-in-the-car/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/apple-wwdc-2013-liveblog8119-1370890081.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2010/07/08/bmw-supports-ipod-out-fills-your-2011-auto-with-2001s-finest-u/\">iPod Out</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/01/30/siri-eyes-free-2013-honda-accord/\">Siri Eyes Free</a> 以外，iOS 产品和轿车间的整合现在又凭借 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/10/ios-7-announced/\">iOS 7</a> 中最新的 iOS in the Car 功能更进了一步。据悉这项功能可以让 iOS 7 和车载系统直接相连，为使用者提供优化的地图、信息和音乐界面。不过想要用上这项功能的话还有待时日，因为包括 Ferrari 在内的多家汽车厂商要等到 2014 年才会推出集成了 iOS in the Car 功能的产品。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/wwdc-2013-ios-in-the-car-0/\">WWDC 2013: iOS in the Car</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/wwdc-2013-ios-in-the-car-0/5950881/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/apple-wwdc-2013-liveblog8120-1370890211_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/wwdc-2013-ios-in-the-car-0/5950882/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/apple-wwdc-2013-liveblog8121-1370890211_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/wwdc-2013-ios-in-the-car-0/5950883/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/apple-wwdc-2013-liveblog8122-1370890212_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/wwdc-2013-ios-in-the-car-0/5950884/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/applewwdc2013-0245-1370890213_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/wwdc-2013-ios-in-the-car-0/5950885/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http: